      "cookedHtml": "<p>I noticed a bug in the mobile application. If the board contains an empty view with a link to the Monday form, when entering text, it is entered from right to left instead of normally from left to right. The video here: <a href=\"https://streamable.com/yom7wp\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Screen_Recording_20240108_141010_mondaycom (1)</a></p>\n<p>The form itself, without a link, only the “native” one, works properly but does not display the logo (WEB and mobile applications).<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/3/03f3acefd866f72547d29dbe1ead6a045ba8f725.png\" title=\"chrome_4dgixWH9Iy\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/3/03f3acefd866f72547d29dbe1ead6a045ba8f725_2_528x500.png\" alt=\"chrome_4dgixWH9Iy\" width=\"528\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">chrome_4dgixWH9Iy</span><span class=\"informations\">658×623 32 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/f/4f56eed7e9ddfdb5c3678797fc63e994e74ffe4f.png\" title=\"chrome_FeM3cMZ17F\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/f/4f56eed7e9ddfdb5c3678797fc63e994e74ffe4f_2_546x500.png\" alt=\"chrome_FeM3cMZ17F\" width=\"546\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">chrome_FeM3cMZ17F</span><span class=\"informations\">707×647 23.4 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
